title: I'm still me
creator_contributor_role: Victoria. Dept. of Human Services, funding
subject_group: Food, Health, Lifestyle, Medicine, Psychology & Safety/People with disabilities
abstract: Brenda's motivation is her love for life
description: Wheel-chair bound is no excuse for Brenda to not get around, to move about - she is motivated and she likes to motivate others. Her philosophy is "I don't know what tomorrow holds so I'll do as much as I can today." This project was funded by the Department of Human Services, (Eastern Metropolitan Region), developed and executed in partnership with MetroAccess at the City of Monash and City of Whitehorse, and Scope.
